title: Eagles-Saints trade-Can Saints compete with Bucs? Targeting DK Metcalf; Receiver Mania
itunes:title: Eagles-Saints trade-Can Saints compete with Bucs? Targeting DK Metcalf; Receiver Mania
description:
The latest edition of The Good Morning Football Podcast breaks down the trade involving draft picks between the New Orleans Saints and Philadelphia Eagles. Hosts Jane Slater, Peter Schrager, Kyle Brandt, and NFL WR Emmanuel Sanders discuss if the New Orleans Saints are in win now mode and can compete with the Tampa Bay Buccaneers. Then they share their thoughts on which teams should target WR DJ Metcalf, they look at the state of the wide receiver position and they finish up with Emmanuel Sanders stories about the quarterbacks he’s played with includes Drew Brees and Peyton Manning.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
